Sentencas: Ni-YSZ composite cermet used as the anode material for solid oxide fuel cell is prepared by electroless technique involving an important sensitization process of YSZ.
Titulo: Ball mill assisted synthesis of Ni-YSZ cermet anode by electroless technique and their characterization

Sentencas: In the present investigation, the sensitization process of YSZ is carried out through cost-effective controlled ball milling.
Titulo: Ball mill assisted synthesis of Ni-YSZ cermet anode by electroless technique and their characterization

Sentencas: The effect of milling speed on electrical, thermal and microstructural properties of such anodes is investigated and optimized at 45 rpm.
Titulo: Ball mill assisted synthesis of Ni-YSZ cermet anode by electroless technique and their characterization

Sentencas: Microstructural analysis of the synthesized Ni-YSZ cermets prepared under the optimized milling conditions showed a core-shell microstructure with YSZ as core and fine metallic Ni particulates as the shell.
Titulo: Ball mill assisted synthesis of Ni-YSZ cermet anode by electroless technique and their characterization

Sentencas: The interconnected metallic Ni creates a conductive pathway at room temperature.
Titulo: Ball mill assisted synthesis of Ni-YSZ cermet anode by electroless technique and their characterization

Sentencas: Such type of unique core-shell anode cermet, results in higher electrical conductivity (sigma(800 degrees C) similar to 500 S/cm) at much lower Ni content (similar to 33 vol%) compared to conventional anode cermet with thermal expansion coefficient (similar to 11.48 x 10(-6) K-1) compatible to other cell components.
Titulo: Ball mill assisted synthesis of Ni-YSZ cermet anode by electroless technique and their characterization
